response.original_title: We Like Girls Project Vol. One
response.overview: Award-winning adult performer Kissa Sins arrived on the set at 11:45 on a bright L.A. morning, barely able to contain her excitement for the scene: a historic pairing between her and industry legend, 2018's Female Performer Of The Year Angela White. Lena Paul and Ivy Labelle are not just adult superstars, they're also in a beautiful lesbian relationship off-camera. And when they found out about We Like Girls, they couldn't wait to get involved.
